name: bitCroSkull
description: bitCroSkull is a commemorative collection of 333 skeletons forever inscribed on the Bitcoin blockchain. All the ordinals are inscribed under the threshold of 1 milion inscriptions and are handmade by the wide-known pixel artist Shadowbright in collaboration with the CroSkull's Team. bitCroSkull is a tribute to our community and ecosystem built on the Cronos Chain, that will also contribute to expand the CroSkull Brand.
